name: Name: the phoenix (ققنوس) | BBR Generative Art
description:
As the first work with the concept of birth from ashes, I present 30 phoenixes as a gift to you dear friends

An artist always creates a work with his worldview and inspiration from his surroundings, so what if we humans give ideas and inspiration to the computer? What is the result of this cooperation? In my opinion, modern art is unpredictable art, art that is born of something beyond the human mind and gaze, a worldview that we have not experienced, and is narrated from the perspective of a computer and artificial intelligence.
